        "timestamp": "2018-05-25 13:16:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nONAP JobBuilder lauched CI.\nBut now problem is in jenkins job configuration\nas tessuite to be run is hardoced in configuration of job:\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/dcaegen2-master-verify-csit-testsuites/configure\nTest are executed by command:\n${WORKSPACE}/test/csit/run-csit.sh ${TESTPLAN} ${TESTOPTIONS}\nbut ${TESTPLAN} is hardcoded to value plans/dcaegen2/testsuites\nso only this test suite would be executed, not all in plans/dcaegen2 as expected.\nCan some one fix/change this configuration?\nThanks",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
